711681f-a.text:
Temple Bruneth Israel, 238 West 23rd Street, north side, between Seventh and Eighth Avenues.

July 18, 1929

From 1860 to about 1920 this was the Third Reformed Presbyterian Church, Reverend F. N. Foster. The Temple acquired the property about 1922. The Church is now located in Tremont.
